=============================================================================
Application Runtime 1.0 Dalvik
=============================================================================

Custom implementation of a Virtual Machine
Take .java to .class and convert it to .dex file
.java (javac) -> .class (dex compiler) -> .dex
ODEX
 An optimized DEX file that is optimized for your device by prelinking
 needed libraries by hardconding their path into the ODEX file
JIT Support <> Just in Time
 Once we load the application for the first time after reboot, we compile the
 DEX bytecode into ARM/x86 instructions set
GC: 2 steps: Mark and Sweep- Pause the Application and GC
An uncompressed DEX file is 30% smaller than compressed JAR

